title: Day 1355
content:
# Day 1355

Was feeling a bit down so I went for a walk. Fixed it!

It's so simple yet we love to overcomplicate things. I'm just as guilty as anyone else of doing this. Yet, all it took was a few miles outside of pushing my son in a stroller and like that all the sadness left my body.

Don't overcomplicate it anon.

12/6/25

Conor Jay Chepenik
